      "message": "Patch Set 3: Looks good to me, approved\n\n(1 inline comment)\n\nLooks OK, but it would be nice to fix up the output of \"lfs getstripe -c\".  We couldn't fix the test immediately, since this would break interoperability testing with old versions of Lustre, but with a good comment explaining the situation in the test we could at least clean it up eventually.",
